<l>aṟattāṟṟi ṉilvāḻkkai yāṟṟiṟ puṟattāṟṟiṟ</l>
<l>pōoyp peṟuva tevaṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If he conduct domestic life upon the path of dharma, by going the other way</l>
